23 (2) The Education Professional Standards Board shall respond to complaints against a
24 certificate holder by the following process:
25 (a) 1. Except as provided in subparagraph 2. of this paragraph, within thirty
26 (30) calendar days of the receipt of a completed complaint, board staff
27 shall conduct an initial review to determine whether there is sufficient
